cast.overview: In 19th century England, Count Dracula travels to London and meets Mina Harker, a young woman who appears as the reincarnation of his lost love.
cast.title: Bram Stoker's Dracula

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia

Jay Robinson (born April 14, 1930) was an American actor specialising in character roles. He was born in New York City, New York.
